2. https://reactjs.co/#basic-preface


Follow the following links for dev environment setup (webpack, babel, react) :-
1. https://www.codementor.io/reactjs/tutorial/beginner-guide-setup-reactjs-environment-npm-babel-6-webpack
2. http://codetheory.in/react-intro-development-environment-setup/




npm install webpack --save
npm install react react-dom --save
npm install babel-loader babel-core babel-preset-es2015 babel-preset-react
npm install babel webpack webpack-dev-server -g
